Feature: Regular expressions
  As a Cucumber student
  I want to learn how to use regular expressions
  So I can match my steps more intelligently

  Scenario: Integer values only
    Given I have entered 50 into the calculator
    And I have entered 70 into the calculator
    And I have entered banana into the calculator

  Scenario: Specific values
    Given Maserati is an Italian car brand
    And Lamborghini is an Italian car brand
    And Volkswagen is an Italian car brand

  Scenario: Singular and plural
    Given I have 2 apples
    And I have 1 apple


